  ('00000000-0000-4003-8003-000000000076', '00000000-0000-4999-8999-000000000002', '00000000-0000-4001-8001-000000000003', 'export controls pressure detected inside ai export controls are shifting from chip lists toward compute governance', 'The tactical implication is not immediate shortage everywhere. It is uneven access, with credible operators securing capacity earlier and weaker buyers absorbing volatility. Policy language is converging, but implementation capacity remains fragmented across jurisdictions. Watch terms: export controls, compute governance, licensing, sovereignty, policy.', 75, array['export controls', 'compute governance', 'licensing', 'sovereignty']::text[], 50, 'Volatile', null, null, now() - interval '52.5 hours', now() - interval '52.5 hours'),
  ('00000000-0000-4003-8003-000000000077', '00000000-0000-4002-8002-000000000003', '00000000-0000-4001-8001-000000000006', 'Operator read: Open-source models are forcing enterprise vendors to justify premium reliability claims', 'Reliability is becoming a board-level control surface. Procurement teams are asking for auditability, escalation policy, and reproducible performance evidence. Open deployments are improving rapidly, but audit and support requirements still favor managed vendors. Watch terms: open models, reliability, licensing, evals, enterprise.', 76, array['open models', 'reliability', 'licensing', 'evals']::text[], 51, 'Constructive', null, null, now() - interval '51.599999999999994 hours', now() - interval '51.599999999999994 hours'),
  ('00000000-0000-4003-8003-000000000078', '00000000-0000-4002-8002-000000000010', '00000000-0000-4001-8001-000000000007', 'procurement is now the measurable constraint in this narrative', 'The strongest Signal is the shift in language from capability to operating cost. That usually precedes budget scrutiny and vendor consolidation. Executives report high AI priority, while operators see slow internal process redesign. Watch terms: enterprise, workflow, procurement, integration, governance.', 77, array['enterprise', 'workflow', 'procurement', 'integration']::text[], 52, 'Constructive', null, null, now() - interval '50.7 hours', now() - interval '50.7 hours'),
  ('00000000-0000-4003-8003-000000000079', '00000000-0000-4002-8002-000000000017', '00000000-0000-4001-8001-000000000008', 'Contradiction watch: Agent reliability is improving in constrained loops, but open-ended autonomy remains brittle.', 'Policy movement is becoming more operational. The next phase is likely reporting obligations, compute accounting, and cross-border enforcement mechanics. Agent reliability is improving in constrained loops, but open-ended autonomy remains brittle. Watch terms: agents, supervision, tools, memory, escalation.', 78, array['agents', 'supervision', 'tools', 'memory']::text[], 53, 'Constructive', null, null, now() - interval '49.8 hours', now() - interval '49.8 hours'),
  ('00000000-0000-4003-8003-000000000080', '00000000-0000-4002-8002-000000000024', '00000000-0000-4001-8001-000000000001', 'Brief candidate: Cloud reserved capacity is masking true accelerator scarcity', 'The market is underestimating integration drag. The model may be ready, but workflow redesign, permissions, and incident handling remain unresolved. Headline availability looks better than enterprise delivery windows for sustained clusters. Watch terms: cloud, reserved capacity, GPU, utilization, pricing.', 79, array['cloud', 'reserved capacity', 'GPU', 'utilization']::text[], 54, 'Constructive', null, null, now() - interval '48.89999999999999 hours', now() - interval '48.89999999999999 hours'),
  ('00000000-0000-4003-8003-000000000081', '00000000-0000-4999-8999-000000000006', '00000000-0000-4001-8001-000000000007', 'reliability pressure detected inside model reliability is becoming a procurement requirement, not an engineering preference', 'Field checks indicate the constraint is no longer a single procurement line item. The relevant operating question is which dependency fails first under sustained demand. Reliability language is standardizing faster than measurement practice. Watch terms: reliability, evals, procurement, audit, SLA.', 80, array['reliability', 'evals', 'procurement', 'audit']::text[], 55, 'Volatile', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475', 'https://example.com/rook-intel/reference', now() - interval '48 hours', now() - interval '48 hours'),
  ('00000000-0000-4003-8003-000000000082', '00000000-0000-4002-8002-000000000007', '00000000-0000-4001-8001-000000000001', 'Operator read: Data-center financing is repricing around power contracts and utilization risk', 'The visible market price is less useful than the delivery window. Operators should track confirmed capacity, power availability, and integration readiness as separate Signals. Capital remains available, but underwriters are scrutinizing power delivery and tenant concentration. Watch terms: financing, PPA, utilization, capex, debt.', 81, array['financing', 'PPA', 'utilization', 'capex']::text[], 72, 'Divergent', null, null, now() - interval '47.099999999999994 hours', now() - interval '47.099999999999994 hours'),
